*if many fighters on either side
  - circle week to side with least fighters

*if many fighters on one side and 1 other other with low stamina/spirit
  - attack fighter with lower spirit/stamina
  - chance relative to how low single fighter stamina/spirit


*if many fighters on one side, 
  - wait for closest fighter to recover or turn his back
  - chance relative to aggression vs intelligence


* if low stamina and spirit and retreating to recover, if comes close to edge, 
  - move along side of edge furthest away from nearest fighter

* if against edge both retreat directions are blocked by fighters
  -if on top btm or edge, attack nearest fighter
  -if on side or diagonal, defend and counter attack

* if trapped between 3 fighters, find best angle to retreat through



